creator: Art Dynasty
descriptionHtml:
Travelers, take a digital journey and discover the ultimate online experience with The Official NEVERSEA Festival App!

The NEVERSEA Festival mobile app can be downloaded for free.
Once you open the digital gateway, you will get connected and inspired by all the Apps insights before, during and after the festival.

All the news regarding the line-up, the performances, the schedule, the tickets or any other general info are at your fingertips! Just download the App and enjoy the exclusive photo gallery, discover the NEVERSEA Beach map and live the magnificent experience of the biggest festival on the Black Sea Shore!

ARTISTS
Check out the amazing names that will perform and warm-up by listening to their music thru the app.

NEWS
Be the first to find out in real time everything new happening at NEVERSEA.

MY LINEUP
Create your schedule and just enjoy the freedom of NEVERSEA. We will take care that you won’t miss your favorite artists, and we will send you through the App a reminder before every show that you’ve selected.

STAGES
Take a journey to all the places you need to be in the four days and nights at NEVERSEA. Find out when are all the NEVERSEA highlights happening in real time.

TICKETS
It's never too late to take the NEVERSEA journey of self-discovery! Here is everything you need to know to grab your ticket.

MAP
Every year NEVERSEA is getting bigger and better! But the festival map will help you get straight to your destination (credit points, food court, bar zone, chillout zone, fun zone, hammock zone, first aid, etc). Take the tour now!

INFO
All the useful info regarding the biggest beach festival on the Black Sea shore, locations and transportation are already set for you.

GALLERY
Be ready to be mesmerized by the spectacular NEVERSEA Beach set at the Black Sea shore.

WALLPAPERS
Travelers, we have a surprise for you! You can now download and use the official NEVERSEA Wallpapers!
